Description: Soplos Plymouth Manager
 A graphical tool to manage Plymouth boot splash themes in SOPLOS Linux.
 Features include:
  * List installed Plymouth themes
  * Preview themes
  * Install new themes from archives
  * Apply themes with one click
  * Modern and intuitive interface
  * Support for multiple languages
